{"tid":2457883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2021年中國「淨網」行動再起　中網友大嘆：乾脆把網路關了","createTime":"2021-03-23T04:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T09:19:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a0495bc0060cc8cf9f43aa486a7663d0342ebbe2","tid":2457883,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"中國網路又將不得安寧！據中國「掃黃打非」辦公室近日發出的訊息，至11月底將展開「<br />\n新風2021」淨網行動，大力掃除淫穢色情低俗、暴力恐怖迷信等有害訊息和出版物，還嚴<br />\n格限制不准直播未經審批的遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n據中國媒體報導指出，全國「掃黃打非」辦公室負責人表示，將以「護苗2021」「凈網<br />\n2021」「秋風2021」專項行動為開展平台。「護苗」行動聚焦育新人使命任務，將集中清<br />\n理夾雜「黃暴毒」、宣揚邪教迷信等有害內容的少兒出版物，清理網上對未成年人具有誘<br />\n導性的不良內容。此外，還會推動學校、家庭嚴格管理學生使用手機等智慧產品。<br />\n <br />\n「淨網」行動涉及的範圍更大，除了將深入整治「直播打賞亂象」，處置低俗直播誘導打<br />\n賞行為；另外還將展開網路遊戲方面的整頓，例如嚴厲打擊傳播淫穢色情、暴力血腥等有<br />\n害內容的網路遊戲、嚴肅處置人物衣著暴露、以打「擦邊球」為噱頭的網路遊戲，以及著<br />\n力查處未經批准擅自運營的網路遊戲、禁止直播未經審批的網路遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n據了解，雖然聲明中表示的是「網路遊戲」，但意思跟台灣玩家熟知的「網路遊戲」有些<br />\n區別。目前中國所有遊戲都是以「網路遊戲」名義接受審批，因此包括單機、手機遊戲在<br />\n內，只要得連上網下載、或是有任何網路功能，通通都算是「網路遊戲」。<br />\n <br />\n消息傳出後，許多中國玩家紛紛大嘆「乾脆把網路整個關了吧」、「直接加速到今年底」<br />\n、「微博那些藏汙納垢的才真的要整頓」、「這不逼人嗎」、「防這防那，把網路關了不<br />\n是更省事？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game.nownews.com/news/20210323/3291007/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20210323%2F3291007%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=15a9e4c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://game.nownews.com/news/20210323/3291007/</a>"},{"pid":"aa19523f8cd7535b9a0ca260f11e5598d94cc22f","tid":2457883,"uid":34666,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:10:43.000Z","msg":"連俾班臭閪蚑那賤蛆打飛機既超大海陸空軍版都封埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e7fcee41ec36f365aecc8970495f4d24194f30","tid":2457883,"uid":21141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"嘴炮完繼續屌美帝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2fdd681b6023e967544fb7b29a68835af5c634","tid":2457883,"uid":393145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"外交官自由去睇AV去TWITTER睇腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daf9c3ff8792a1fd15fc98565cd75b62f1530a8","tid":2457883,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"直接轉左intranet咪算"},{"pid":"4364ad712c62021b738ba4bd6566b6e09d6c73d3","tid":2457883,"uid":121197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"封完你班契弟咪又係用VPN翻牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8172521a627c6d1def84f248e97d0193663d8d9","tid":2457883,"uid":19660,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"戇鳩大陸佬，你以為網絡有開過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea4116030899ffb82f8ca400b0491df7d3ee37a","tid":2457883,"uid":394244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8172521a627c6d1def84f248e97d0193663d8d9","tid":2457883,"uid":19660,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"戇鳩大陸佬，你以為網絡有開過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00390af85044cbb4cec415f5786f8909ce5684c","tid":2457883,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"直接內聯網算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95057499b67c8ac70b1e1054655f703cd30f091a","tid":2457883,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T